            <title><![CDATA[Microsoft announces Xbox Partner Preview for this week, with Ryu Ga Gotoku's Stranger Than Heaven finally making a showing]]></title>
            <link>https://www.eurogamer.net/microsoft-announces-xbox-partner-preview-for-this-week-with-ryu-ga-gotokus-stranger-than-heaven-finally-making-a-showing</link>
